  "texts": [
    "Figure 3 illustrates the emerging technologies in IoT for agriculture, including AI, blockchain, drones, big data analytics, robotics, 5G connectivity, and edge computing to make informed decisions for improved yield and efficiency (Shaikh et al. 2022).",
    "These trends highlight the potential of IoT to revolutionize modern agricultural practices.",
    "Farmers are currently facing various challenges, including the need to produce more food with limited resources to feed a growing global population, minimize environmental impact, adapt to rising global temperatures, cope with water and energy shortages, and meet the preferences of a tech-savvy generation of digital natives.",
    "Here, we explore some of these emerging technologies in agriculture.",
    "Artificial intelligence (AI) Artificial intelligence is a rapidly evolving field that is gaining global attention."
